sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant A as 交互接入层
    participant O as 编排控制层
    participant S as Run State
    participant G as 治理层
    participant H as 审批人 / HITL
    participant T as 工具运行时

    O->>S: 保存 question_id=q12 与 waiting_for_user
    O-->>A: clarification.request q12 + options + expiry
    A-->>U: 可访问问题与选择
    U->>A: clarification.response q12
    A->>A: 校验 identity session question_id expiry
    A->>O: 规范化答案 + response_id
    O->>S: 幂等提交答案并恢复 Running
    O->>G: 高风险 ActionIntent + action_digest=h9
    G-->>O: require_approval policy=p17
    O->>S: checkpoint cp9 + waiting_approval + digest
    O-->>H: approval.request ap7 + 摘要 + 有效期
    alt 批准
        H-->>O: approve ap7 + digest=h9
        O->>G: 重验 identity resource digest policy expiry
        G-->>O: allow + decision_ref
        O->>T: execute with idempotency_key
        T-->>O: typed observation + effect receipt
        O->>S: commit observation and continue
    else 拒绝
        H-->>O: deny ap7 + reason
        O->>S: record denied and replan / stop
    else 过期或关键参数变化
        O->>S: invalidate ap7
        O-->>A: approval_expired / request again
        A-->>U: 展示新摘要或安全终止
    end
